the presence of features\nnear the polar regions and/or strong features in the flow field in general. If\nconvergence is of concern and the simulation contains strong dynamics, then\ngrids which are based on the geodesic polyhedron are recommended compared to\nmore conventionally used UV-mapped meshes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 28 Feb 2022 11:32:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-06"}
