en an incorrect cosmology has been assumed in their\nconstruction. Given that the turnover is related to the horizon scale at\nmatter-radiation equality, a sufficiently precise constraint of $k_0$ presents\nthe possibility for a novel probe of cosmology. We therefore present a\npotential methodology for constructing a standard-ruler-based distance\nmeasurement, independent of the sound horizon, using the turnover location in\nthe HI power spectrum.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 28 Feb 2022 14:37:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 24 Mar 2022 12:07:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-25"}
